    <item>
      <title>[工具] LaTex</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/post/%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/latex/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 May 2026 00:00:00 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <author>xxx@example.com (byzh)</author>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/post/%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/latex/</guid>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>[工具] LaTex</h1><p>作者：byzh（xxx@example.com）</p>
        
          <h1 id="报告模版">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e6%8a%a5%e5%91%8a%e6%a8%a1%e7%89%88"></a>
报告模版
</h1><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-tex" data-lang="tex"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% 1. 基础文档与中文支持（Overleaf专用，修复生僻字）
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\documentclass</span><span class="na">[UTF8,fontset=none]</span><span class="nb">{</span>ctexart<span class="nb">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% Overleaf 原生预装 Noto 思源字体，完整支持“焜”等生僻字
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\setCJKmainfont</span><span class="nb">{</span>Noto Serif CJK SC<span class="nb">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\setCJKsansfont</span><span class="nb">{</span>Noto Sans CJK SC<span class="nb">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\setCJKmonofont</span><span class="nb">{</span>Noto Sans Mono CJK SC<span class="nb">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% 2. 页面布局与边距设置
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\usepackage</span><span class="nb">{</span>geometry<span class="nb">}</span>              <span class="c">% 页面尺寸、边距控制
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\geometry</span><span class="nb">{</span>a4paper, left=2.5cm, right=2.5cm, top=2.5cm, bottom=2.5cm<span class="nb">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% 3. 数学公式与符号
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\usepackage</span><span class="nb">{</span>amsmath<span class="nb">}</span>               <span class="c">% 数学公式核心扩展包
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\usepackage</span><span class="nb">{</span>amssymb<span class="nb">}</span>               <span class="c">% 数学符号与字体扩展
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% 4. 表格绘制增强
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\usepackage</span><span class="nb">{</span>multirow<span class="nb">}</span>              <span class="c">% 表格单元格跨行
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\usepackage</span><span class="nb">{</span>tabularx<span class="nb">}</span>              <span class="c">% 自动宽度表格
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\usepackage</span><span class="nb">{</span>booktabs<span class="nb">}</span>              <span class="c">% 专业表格横线（三线表）
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% 5. 列表环境（枚举/项目符）
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\usepackage</span><span class="nb">{</span>enumitem<span class="nb">}</span>              <span class="c">% 自定义列表缩进、标签、间距
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% 6. 图片与图形绘制
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\usepackage</span><span class="nb">{</span>float<span class="nb">}</span>                 <span class="c">% 浮动体（图表）位置控制（H选项）
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\usepackage</span><span class="nb">{</span>graphicx<span class="nb">}</span>              <span class="c">% 插入图片必备
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\usepackage</span><span class="nb">{</span>tikz<span class="nb">}</span>                  <span class="c">% 矢量绘图与精确定位
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\usepackage</span><span class="nb">{</span>eso-pic<span class="nb">}</span>               <span class="c">% 页面背景/水印/绝对定位图片
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% 7. 页眉页脚样式
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\usepackage</span><span class="nb">{</span>fancyhdr<span class="nb">}</span>              <span class="c">% 自定义页眉、页脚、页码
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% 8. 代码高亮与展示
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\usepackage</span><span class="nb">{</span>listings<span class="nb">}</span>              <span class="c">% 基础代码环境
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\usepackage</span><span class="nb">{</span>xcolor<span class="nb">}</span>                <span class="c">% 颜色定义支持
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\usepackage</span><span class="nb">{</span>minted<span class="nb">}</span>                <span class="c">% 高级代码高亮（依赖Python/Pygments）
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\usemintedstyle</span><span class="nb">{</span>colorful<span class="nb">}</span>          <span class="c">% minted代码高亮风格
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% 9. 高亮框与内容美化
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\usepackage</span><span class="na">[most]</span><span class="nb">{</span>tcolorbox<span class="nb">}</span>       <span class="c">% 彩色边框/背景盒子，most开启全部功能
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% 10. 超链接与书签（必须放最后）
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\usepackage</span><span class="na">[hidelinks]</span><span class="nb">{</span>hyperref<span class="nb">}</span>   <span class="c">% 交叉引用、目录链接，hidelinks隐藏边框
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ============================================================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% 全局配置
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ============================================================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% 页眉页脚设置（fancyhdr 包）
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\pagestyle</span><span class="nb">{</span>fancy<span class="nb">}</span>                  <span class="c">% 启用fancy页眉页脚样式，替代默认格式
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\fancyhf</span><span class="nb">{}</span>                         <span class="c">% 清空当前所有页眉、页脚内容，避免默认样式干扰
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\renewcommand</span><span class="nb">{</span><span class="k">\headrulewidth</span><span class="nb">}{</span>0pt<span class="nb">}</span> <span class="c">% 取消页眉下方的默认横线，让页面更简洁
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\fancyfoot</span><span class="na">[C]</span><span class="nb">{</span><span class="k">\thepage</span><span class="nb">}</span>            <span class="c">% 页脚居中位置显示当前页码（C=Center居中）
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% 文档标题、作者、日期定义
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\title</span><span class="nb">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="k">\Huge</span> <span class="k">\textbf</span><span class="nb">{</span>西安电子科技大学<span class="nb">}</span> 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="k">\\</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="k">\vspace</span><span class="nb">{</span>0.3cm<span class="nb">}</span>                     
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ——<span class="k">\LARGE</span> 图像处理与机器视觉~大作业           
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nb">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\author</span><span class="nb">{}</span>         <span class="c">% 作者栏留空
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\date</span><span class="nb">{}</span>           <span class="c">% 日期栏留空
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\begin</span><span class="nb">{</span>document<span class="nb">}</span> <span class="c">%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% 封面左上角插入校徽logo
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\AddToShipoutPicture*</span><span class="nb">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="k">\AtPageUpperLeft</span><span class="nb">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="k">\begin</span><span class="nb">{</span>tikzpicture<span class="nb">}</span>[remember picture, overlay]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">            <span class="k">\node</span><span class="na">[anchor=north west, inner sep=0pt]</span> at (1cm,-1cm) <span class="nb">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">                <span class="k">\includegraphics</span><span class="na">[width=3cm]</span><span class="nb">{</span>src/xd<span class="nb">_</span>local.png<span class="nb">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">            <span class="nb">}</span>;
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="k">\end</span><span class="nb">{</span>tikzpicture<span class="nb">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="nb">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nb">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% 生成标题页
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\maketitle</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% 实验名称
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\begin</span><span class="nb">{</span>center<span class="nb">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="k">\Huge</span> 实验名称: <span class="k">\textbf</span><span class="nb">{</span>基于GAN的图像风格转换<span class="nb">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="k">\\</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="k">\vspace</span><span class="nb">{</span>0.5cm<span class="nb">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="k">\Large</span> ———— ~ CycleGAN实现“马→斑马”
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\end</span><span class="nb">{</span>center<span class="nb">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\vspace</span><span class="nb">{</span>1cm<span class="nb">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% 个人信息
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\begin</span><span class="nb">{</span>center<span class="nb">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="k">\Large</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="k">\begin</span><span class="nb">{</span>tabular<span class="nb">}{</span>ll<span class="nb">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        学院: <span class="nb">&amp;</span> <span class="k">\underline</span><span class="nb">{</span>人工智能<span class="nb">}</span><span class="k">\\</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="nb">&amp;</span> <span class="k">\\</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        行政班: <span class="nb">&amp;</span> <span class="k">\underline</span><span class="nb">{</span>2320032<span class="nb">}</span><span class="k">\\</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="nb">&amp;</span> <span class="k">\\</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        教学班: <span class="nb">&amp;</span> <span class="k">\underline</span><span class="nb">{</span>AI205003 | 02班<span class="nb">}</span><span class="k">\\</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="nb">&amp;</span> <span class="k">\\</span>
