</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">A[开始] --&gt; B{判断}
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">B --&gt; |是| C[执行]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">B --&gt; |否| D[结束]
</span></span></code></pre></div><pre class="mermaid">
  graph TD
A[开始] --> B{判断}
B --> |是| C[执行]
B --> |否| D[结束]
</pre>
        
